    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-01-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-02-09T15:09:14Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to treat certain controlled foreign corporations created or organized under the laws of a tax-haven country as domestic corporations for tax purposes. Sets forth a list of &quot;tax-haven countries&quot; and grants the Secretary of the Treasury authority to remove or add a country from such list. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>A bill to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to treat controlled foreign corporations in tax havens as domestic corporations.</title>
